column13:
A machine for opening or initiating the opening of a package comprising: 
means for guiding the package (10,16,18) along a selected path; 
means (36) for opening or initiating the opening of the package (10,16,18) as the package travels forward along the path; 
means for detecting the opening or the initiation of the opening of the package (10,16,18); and 
means (60) responsive to said detecting means for recording the occurrence of the opening or the initiation of the opening of the package.
